. Future-Proofing for GenAI
To prepare for Agentic AI (e.g., a chatbot that says "Show me all layers related to wind energy in Stuttgart"), we have already:

Isolated the Backend: Your FastAPI app can later integrate libraries like LangChain or OpenAI easily.

Vector Ready: PostGIS (your database) is actually excellent at storing "Vector Embeddings" (AI data) using an extension called pgvector. You won't need a separate database for your AI features later.